title: Lunchbox Returns After Having Another Baby + Favorite Reality Star Draft + Bobby Tells People To Calm Down About Coronavirus
itunes:title: Lunchbox Returns After Having Another Baby + Favorite Reality Star Draft + Bobby Tells People To Calm Down About Coronavirus
description:
Lunchbox is back in studio after welcoming his second baby! He gives an update on how their home life has changed with a new baby boy. Also, we do our Bobby Bones Show draft on favorite reality television stars. Plus, Bobby goes on a rant urging people to calm down about all the coronavirus news coverage!
